/a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<nav class=\"provisional gc-subway\">\n<h1 id=\"gc-document-nav\">Francophone Minority Communities Student Pilot</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/eligibility.html#_Language_tests\">Who can apply</a> <a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/eligibility.html#_Language_tests\">Who can apply</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/eligibility/participating-dlis.html\">Participating designated learning institutions and financial requirement</a> <a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/eligibility/participating-dlis.html\">Participating designated learning institutions and financial requirement</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/get-documents.html\">Get the right documents</a> <a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/get-documents.html\">Get the right documents</a></li>\n<li><a aria-current=\"page\" class=\"active\" href=\"#\">How to apply</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/after-apply.html\">After you apply</a> <a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/after-apply.html\">After you apply</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/path-to-pr.html\">Path to permanent residence</a> <a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/path-to-pr.html\">Path to permanent residence</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n<h1 id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">How to apply</h1>\n<p>Before you apply online, make sure you have the following:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/application-forms-guides/guide-5269-applying-study-permit-outside-canada.html\">instruction guide</a> to fill out your forms</li>\n<li>scanner or camera to create electronic copies of your documents</li>\n<li>valid <a aria-controls=\"centred-popup1\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#centred-popup1\" role=\"button\">credit</a> or <a aria-controls=\"centred-popup2\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#centred-popup2\" role=\"button\">debit</a> card to make a payment</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"h3\" id=\"instructions\">Get instructions to apply online</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<!-- FIELDFLOW starts here  -->\n<div class=\"wb-fieldflow\" data-wb-fieldflow='{\n                \"hideelm\": \"#no\",\n                \"reset\": { \"action\": \"addClass\", \"source\":\"#no,.cname\", \"class\": \"hidden\" }\n            }'>\n<p class=\"mrgn-tp-lg\">Select your country of citizenship from this list of eligible countries to get your local visa office and online application instructions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#benin, #no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Bénin</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#burkinafaso,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Burkina Faso</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#burundi,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Burundi</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#cabo,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Cabo Verde</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#cameroon,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Cameroon</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#african,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Central African Republic</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#chad,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Chad</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#comoros,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Comoros</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#cote,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Côte d´Ivoire</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#congo,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Democratic Republic of the Congo</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#dominica,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Dominica</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#republic-congo,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Republic of the Congo</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#djibouti,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Djibouti</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#egypt,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Egypt</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#equatorial-guinea,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Equatorial Guinea</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#gabon,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Gabon</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#guinea,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Guinea</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#guinea-bissau,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Guinea-Bissau</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#haiti,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Haïti</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#lebanon,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Lebanon</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#madagascar,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Madagascar</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#mali,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Mali</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#mauritania,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Mauritania</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#mauritius,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Mauritius</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#morocco,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Morocco</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#niger,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Niger</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#rwanda,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Rwanda</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#saint-lucia,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Saint Lucia</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#sao-tome,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">São Tomé and Principe</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#senegal,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Senegal</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#seychelles,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Seychelles</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#togo,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Togo</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#tunisia,#no\"}'><a href=\"#no\">Tunisia</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"nojs-hide\">\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"benin\">\n<h3>For citizens of Bénin</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"burkinafaso\">\n<h3>For citizens of Burkina Faso</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"burundi\">\n<h3>For citizens of Burundi</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"cabo\">\n<h3>For citizens of Cabo Verde</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"cameroon\">\n<h3>For citizens of Cameroon</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"african\">\n<h3>For citizens of Central African Republic</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"chad\">\n<h3>For citizens of Chad</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"comoros\">\n<h3>For citizens of Comoros</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"cote\">\n<h3>For citizens of Côte d'Ivoire</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"congo\">\n<h3>For citizens of Democratic Republic of the Congo</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"dominica\">\n<h3>For citizens of Dominica</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"republic-congo\">\n<h3>For citizens of Republic of the Congo</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"djibouti\">\n<h3>For citizens of Djibouti</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"egypt\">\n<h3>For citizens of Egypt</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"equatorial-guinea\">\n<h3>For citizens of Equatorial Guinea</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"gabon\">\n<h3>For citizens of Gabon</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"guinea\">\n<h3>For citizens of Guinea</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"guinea-bissau\">\n<h3>For citizens of Guinea-Bissau</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"haïti\">\n<h3>For residents of Haïti</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"lebanon\">\n<h3>For citizens of Lebanon</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"madagascar\">\n<h3>For residents of Madagascar</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"mali\">\n<h3>For citizens of Mali</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"mauritania\">\n<h3>For citizens of Mauritania</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"mauritius\">\n<h3>For citizens of Mauritius</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"morocco\">\n<h3>For citizens of Morocco</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"niger\">\n<h3>For citizens of Niger</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"rwanda\">\n<h3>For citizens of Rwanda</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"saint-lucia\">\n<h3>For citizens of Saint Lucia</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"sao-tome\">\n<h3>For citizens of São Tomé and Principe</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"senegal\">\n<h3>For citizens of Senegal</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"seychelles\">\n<h3>For citizens of Seychelles</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"togo\">\n<h3>For citizens of Togo</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden cname\" id=\"tunisia\">\n<h3>For citizens of Tunisia</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"no\">\n<h2 class=\"nojs-show\">If you are not applying with a family member who is applying for a work permit</h2>\n<p>You must apply online. You need an account to apply online.</p>\n<p>You can use your account to</p>\n<ul>\n<li>pay your fees</li>\n<li>submit your application</li>\n<li>check the status of your application</li>\n</ul>\n<p>When you apply, make sure you</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n            select “Yes, I meet an exception from submitting a provincial or territorial attestation letter” when asked, “<strong>Do you have a provincial or territorial attestation letter or meet an exception from submitting a provincial or territorial attestation letter</strong>”\n        </li>\n<li>\n            include all the\n            <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/get-documents.html\">documents you need</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n            submit your language test results\n            <ul>\n<li>\n                    Submit your language test results through the IRCC secure account by uploading them in the\n                    <strong>Proof of Language Test Results</strong>\n                    field.\n                </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n            follow your visa office instructions in case you need to provide other documents:\n            <ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/pdf/kits/forms/IMM5826E.pdf\">Document checklist – Study permit [IMM 5826] (PDF, 140 KB)</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-success\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/account.html\">Create an account or sign in</a></p>\n</div>\n<!--  FIELDFLOW ends here -->\n<nav class=\"gc-subway-pagination\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Document navigation</h2>\n<ul class=\"pager\">\n<li class=\"next\">\n<a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/after-apply.html\" rel=\"next\">\n<span class=\"wb-inv\">Next:</span>\n                After you apply\n            </a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"credit-debit-payment-eng\"></span>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"centred-popup1\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<p class=\"h5 modal-title\">Credit cards and prepaid cards</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p>We accept credit cards and prepaid cards from:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visa<sup>®</sup> </li>\n<li>MasterCard<sup>®</sup> </li>\n<li>American Express<sup>®</sup> </li>\n<li>JCB<sup>®</sup> </li>\n<li>UnionPay<sup>®</sup> (for online applications only; debit cards not accepted)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you use a prepaid credit card, keep it for <strong>at least</strong> 18 months after you pay to make refunds easier. <a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?qnum=1215&amp;top=4\">Find more on prepaid cards</a>.</p>\n<p>We also accept all Visa Debit cards.The card you use doesn't have to be in your name. The cardholder’s name will appear on the receipt but it does not need to match your application.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"centred-popup2\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<p class=\"h5 modal-title\">Debit cards</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p>It must:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>be from a Canadian bank using <a href=\"http://www.interac.ca/en/interac-online-consumer.html\">INTERAC<sup>®</sup> Online</a>, and</li>\n<li>be registered for online banking through your bank’s website.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We also accept all Debit MasterCard<sup>®</sup> and Visa<sup>®</sup> Debit cards. If your card has the Visa Debit logo on it, alone or with the INTERAC<sup>®</sup> Online logo, select Visa Debit as your payment method.</p>\n<p>The card you use does not have to be in your name. The cardholder’s name will appear on the receipt but it does not need to match your application.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2026-02-10\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-footer\">\n<footer id=\"wb-info\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Abou